==English==
===Etymology===
From Urdu {{URchar|[[جگناته]]}} (jagannāth), former name of [[w:Puri|Puri]] in India, where the material came from.  Compare [[juggernaut]].

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/ˈʤækənɪt/}}

